## â–¶ï¸ How to Run

### ğŸ“¦ Prerequisites
- Java 17+
- Maven installed (`mvn -v`)
- Chrome / Firefox / Edge browser installed
- Allure CLI installed (optional for viewing report)
- Jenkins installed (optional for CI/CD)


### ğŸ§ª Run Tests and Genrate Allure Report
```bash
mvn clean test ; mvn allure:report
```

### ğŸ“Š Generate Allure Report
```bash
mvn allure:report
```

### ğŸ‘€ View Report
```bash
allure serve target/site/allure-maven-plugin
```

